column2: SELECT SpecObj.specObjID, SpecObj.z, SpecObj.ra, SpecObj.dec, SpecObj.sourceType, SpecObj.class, zooSpec.p_el, zooSpec.p_cw, zooSpec.p_acw, zooSpec.p_mg FROM SpecObj, zooSpec WHERE zooSpec.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID AND SpecObj.class = # AND SpecObj.sourceType = # ORDER BY SpecObj.z DESC
